title: Match History Not Updating -___-
body: My most recent game isn't appearing on my match history. I fear I didn't get the points & etc. from my match now. I did so good too ; - ; Is there anyway to fix this??

replies.body:
Hey there,

It's possible the server just needs time to catch up, if the game still doesn't appear in your match history after 24-48 hours then it's possible the game was lost.

This happens sometimes and unfortunately, there's no way to recover the game.
